fields.name: ClientEncryptionKeyId
fields.description: The identifier of the Client Encryption Key to be used to encrypt the path.

fields.name: EncryptionAlgorithm
fields.description: The encryption algorithm which will be used. Eg - AEAD_AES_256_CBC_HMAC_SHA256.

fields.name: EncryptionType
fields.description: The type of encryption to be performed. Eg - Deterministic, Randomized.

fields.name: Path
fields.description: Path that needs to be encrypted.
